<h3>Best Places to Ski in February</h3>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">If you're looking for snow, plan your holiday for February. It's considered the snowiest month of the season because it's consistently blanketed in perfect powder. As the month draws to a close, daylight hours are longer and temperatures are milder, so you can ski for more hours each day!</p>
