<h3>Best Places to Ski in March</h3>
<p>One of the biggest benefits of skiing in March is the weather - who doesn't love a bluebird day? You'll also see lots of different types of snow in March - from soft to hard packed - making it a good month to practice a wide range of skiing skills.</p>
