<h3>Best Places to Ski in April</h3>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">April is an ideal time to visit the slopes because of the sunny days, favourable temperatures, and small crowds. A family skiing holiday in spring is a great way to introduce your children to the joys of winter. The snow conditions are perfect for making progressive, smooth turns.</p>
