<h3>Book your <a data-udi="umb://document/c511f5b016b94e78afe01f1584da0f77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c511f5b016b94e78afe01f1584da0f77}" title="Ski 2022 2023 Holidays">2022/2023 ski holiday</a> with confidence, read on for some reviews from our guests last season. </h3>
<p><strong>Colin - <a data-udi="umb://document/f83067c81c00418c8388dd8dcb5bb92d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83067c81c00418c8388dd8dcb5bb92d}" title="Hotel Steiner">Hotel Steiner</a> - April 2022</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our Ingams holiday was fantastic at the Hotel Steiner in Obertauern. Hotel was amazing and Katherine our rep was more than helpful and nothing was too much trouble, even on her day off, when we needed help and information, after I ended up with a dislocated fracture. I would definitely recommend the hotel and will definitely be using Inghams again.</span></p>
<p><strong>Paul - <a data-udi="umb://document/40ee75dda3d24f7fa43e5f94dcd3cad1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/40ee75dda3d24f7fa43e5f94dcd3cad1}" title="Chalet Arktic">Chalet Arktic</a> - March 2022</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Helpful support, going beyond by looking for resort info and suggesting property to suit. Used Inghams many times and will continue to do so.</span></p>
<p><strong>Claire D - <a data-udi="umb://document/6b447f439b0c47be9d609e5b845c8d73" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6b447f439b0c47be9d609e5b845c8d73}" title="Hotel Solaria">Hotel Solaria</a> - April 2022</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Amazing holiday in Ischgl from start to finish. The hotel was beautiful and the food, hospitality and location perfect. All the staff at the hotel went above and beyond. All seamless from start to finish from transport to slopes. Would definitely repeat the whole holiday.</span></p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.feefo.com/en-GB/reviews/inghams?displayFeedbackType=BOTH&amp;timeFrame=YEAR" target="_blank" title="Inghams Feefo Reviews" data-anchor="?displayFeedbackType=BOTH&amp;timeFrame=YEAR"><span style="font-weight: 400;">View all reviews &gt;&gt;</span></a></p>
